  "1691190": {
    "name": "Rogue Waters",
    "steam_appid": 1691190,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/f801891a214ddc60db839f13efb273d2.poster.avif?t=1748339686\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/f801891a214ddc60db839f13efb273d2.webm?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/f801891a214ddc60db839f13efb273d2.mp4?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为海盗船长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为<strong><i>卡特船长</i></strong>，扬帆起航，深陷权力争斗与复仇困境之中，与命运殊死搏斗。在危险的海域中航行，释放神话中的海洋生物，用智慧击败敌人，追逐传奇宝藏，最终揭开黑暗谜团。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一段充满忠诚、背叛与复仇的旅程，揭开海洋守护者预言的神秘面纱，并面对具有不死之身的<strong><i>布莱克博恩船长</i></strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每次冒险前，用你的<strong>海盗洞穴</strong><i>（老巢）</i>来<strong>装备船只升级和船员</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险都会带来新的遭遇战，越是接近布莱克博恩船长，越需要你谨慎航行。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽情享受这个以丰富故事驱动的冒险之旅吧！它分为三个章节，经得起无数次重玩的考验。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/e0c0e79d43dd603a3cb8fd37260da070.poster.avif?t=1748339686\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/e0c0e79d43dd603a3cb8fd37260da070.webm?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/e0c0e79d43dd603a3cb8fd37260da070.mp4?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >集结你的船员</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募并培养你的海盗船员团队，带领他们战斗，并在过程中中发掘他们隐藏的潜能。他们注定要成为传奇海盗，而你的责任就是把他们塑造成这样的传奇。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从<strong>6个独特的职业</strong>中招募，每个职业都有不同的能力和玩法，为你的团队增添多样性。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险之后，你可以<strong>升级船员的技能</strong>，提升他们的战斗效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>伤害会在每次冒险后继续存在</strong>，因此你需要更换船员，让他们有时间疗伤。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/c89f93cf5db2d72c7ae1dbe464627eb7.poster.avif?t=1748339686\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/c89f93cf5db2d72c7ae1dbe464627eb7.webm?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/c89f93cf5db2d72c7ae1dbe464627eb7.mp4?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >变幻莫测的陆地和海洋</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着每次冒险，游戏世界也会发生程序性的变化，这会让你不断面对新的挑战，带来全新的秘密，还有完全不同的战斗场景和独特的宝藏供你探索。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 遭遇战中有多种多样的海盗派别和敌人类型，所以你需要<i>明智地选择你的战斗</i>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的船员会与<strong>船只和陆地</strong>上的敌人交战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>访问商店</strong>进行治疗、升级船员、购买大炮，以及修理船只。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以<strong>勒索商店以获取战利品</strong>，但这会导致一场战斗。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/bf781d47d29a7113f056882f141119cf.poster.avif?t=1748339686\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/bf781d47d29a7113f056882f141119cf.webm?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/bf781d47d29a7113f056882f141119cf.mp4?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扭转乾坤</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过大炮和舰船火炮自定义你的海上遭遇战。在海战中释放强力攻击，摧毁敌舰组件，在登船战斗中占据上风。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遭遇战从海战开始，你可以使用大炮瞄准敌船的关键部位。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的船只和敌船都有独具特色的增强效果，可以被摧毁。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >船员在战斗中可能会成为目标被杀死，因此在登船前要保护好你的船只和船员。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/34e0c7e46fe846cbc53d891722e8c287.poster.avif?t=1748339686\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/34e0c7e46fe846cbc53d891722e8c287.webm?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/34e0c7e46fe846cbc53d891722e8c287.mp4?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >值得揣摩的战术</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验开展回合式战斗的一种全新方式，重现惊险刺激的秘密决斗。使用环境获得前所未有的优势。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>登船阶段</strong>，你和你的船员将与敌人展开徒手搏斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用船员的独特能力来<strong>操纵敌人，并将他们逼至障碍物</strong>，造成致命伤害。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>利用环境</strong>，将敌人推向尖刺，拾取一次性武器，或用绳索摆动到有利位置。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/a330622a5e783fc724baa025670380f3.poster.avif?t=1748339686\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/a330622a5e783fc724baa025670380f3.webm?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/a330622a5e783fc724baa025670380f3.mp4?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >召唤深海生灵</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾被认为是神话的传奇海洋生物在《Rogue Waters》的海洋中游荡。帮助它们摆脱囚禁的命运，获取它们的信任，在战斗中召唤它们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在登船阶段中召唤3只海怪来协助战斗：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>克拉肯</strong>会粉碎周边的敌人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>人鱼</strong>会扰乱敌人，并将他们推向任意方向。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>巨型海蜗牛</strong>可以在甲板上放置致命尖刺障碍物。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/f31ed747e8c5d08fbfbd1e4532c383d1.poster.avif?t=1748339686\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/f31ed747e8c5d08fbfbd1e4532c383d1.webm?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1691190/extras/f31ed747e8c5d08fbfbd1e4532c383d1.mp4?t=1748339686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻肉鸽型海盗冒险</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险都会重置你的装备和物品，但会解锁你的船员、船只，和卡特船长的永久升级，让你在每次战斗中都变得更强大。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次挑战之间，物品和升级都会重置：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>个人物品</strong>（角色装备）：额外武器、攻击修饰词，以及技能的额外升级。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>舰载武器</strong>（大炮和类似物品）：每次新的冒险都以可用的基础入门装备开始。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>船只组件</strong>也会重置。</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每次冒险都会永久提升你的进度：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为船员和卡特船长<strong>解锁技能树</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在海盗洞穴（老巢）中获得<strong>船只和港口升级设施</strong>。</p></li></ul></li></ul>",
